or that movie that's coming out in two years!don't be jealous. remember the good things of your life, but don't keep in negativity. sing, dance, and treat your body right because you never know when you'll lose it, and if you do, all you'll think about is how you didn't use it the way you should have. be humble and learn to be nice to the people that give love and care to you, not just the strangers you meet. don't think that you'll always have everything...or something.take bad people out of your life. teach people that they have to respect a fair lady like you. don't let anyone disrespect you, especially your partner or child. try not to be a bad person; don't be a bad person at all. learn from your mistakes and remember we all make mistakes.don't be afraid to love what you love. don't try to like something or support something 'cause everyone else does. learn to love and appreciate yourself before you ask anyone to love and support you. be yourself because you are extraordinary and unique.
